        "text": "Done! Here's what changed:\n\n### ⭐ Starfish Shape\nThe 5 LEDs are now arranged like a starfish radiating from a center point:\n```\n        [Top]         col 4, row 0\n  [Top-Left]  [Top-Right]   cols 1 & 7, row 4\n  [Bot-Left]  [Bot-Right]   cols 2 & 6, row 10\n```\nSymmetrical star shape — 2 arms up, 2 arms mid-spread, 1 arm top-center.\n\n### 💡 Sketch\nAll 5 LEDs now blink **together in sync** — 500ms ON, 500ms OFF, repeating forever. No more ripple or twinkle patterns."
